SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[TaskStatus], [t].[Comment], [t].[DeadLine], [t].[EntryDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AccessFailedCount], [t0].[AuthenticationSource], [t0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[DeleterUserId], [t0].[DeletionTime], [t0].[EmailAddress], [t0].[EmailConfirmationCode], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsEmailConfirmed], [t0].[IsLockoutEnabled], [t0].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [t0].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [t0].[LastModificationTime], [t0].[LastModifierUserId], [t0].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [t0].[Name], [t0].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [t0].[NormalizedUserName], [t0].[Password], [t0].[PasswordResetCode], [t0].[PhoneNumber], [t0].[SecurityStamp], [t0].[Surname], [t0].[TenantId], [t0].[UserName]
FROM (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Comment], [d].[DeadLine], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[EntryDate], [d].[Name], [d].[TaskStatus]
    FROM [DailyTasks] AS [d]
    WHERE (((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([d].[EmployeeId] = @__AbpSession_UserId_0)
    ORDER BY [d].[Name]
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[AuthenticationSource], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[DeleterUserId], [a].[DeletionTime], [a].[EmailAddress], [a].[EmailConfirmationCode], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsEmailConfirmed], [a].[IsLockoutEnabled], [a].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[Password], [a].[PasswordResetCode], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[Surname], [a].[TenantId], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [AbpUsers] AS [a]
    WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ((@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_3))
) AS [t0] ON [t].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Name]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[TaskStatus], [t].[Comment], [t].[DeadLine], [t].[EntryDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AccessFailedCount], [t0].[AuthenticationSource], [t0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[DeleterUserId], [t0].[DeletionTime], [t0].[EmailAddress], [t0].[EmailConfirmationCode], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsEmailConfirmed], [t0].[IsLockoutEnabled], [t0].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [t0].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [t0].[LastModificationTime], [t0].[LastModifierUserId], [t0].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [t0].[Name], [t0].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [t0].[NormalizedUserName], [t0].[Password], [t0].[PasswordResetCode], [t0].[PhoneNumber], [t0].[SecurityStamp], [t0].[Surname], [t0].[TenantId], [t0].[UserName], CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [UpdatedDailyTasks] AS [u]
        WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([u].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([t].[Id] = [u].[DailyTaskId])) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
FROM (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Comment], [d].[DeadLine], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[EntryDate], [d].[Name], [d].[TaskStatus]
    FROM [DailyTasks] AS [d]
    WHERE (((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([d].[EmployeeId] = @__AbpSession_UserId_0)
    ORDER BY [d].[Name]
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

(DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[TaskStatus], [t].[Comment], [t].[DeadLine], [t].[EntryDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AccessFailedCount], [t0].[AuthenticationSource], [t0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[DeleterUserId], [t0].[DeletionTime], [t0].[EmailAddress], [t0].[EmailConfirmationCode], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsEmailConfirmed], [t0].[IsLockoutEnabled], [t0].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [t0].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [t0].[LastModificationTime], [t0].[LastModifierUserId], [t0].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [t0].[Name], [t0].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [t0].[NormalizedUserName], [t0].[Password], [t0].[PasswordResetCode], [t0].[PhoneNumber], [t0].[SecurityStamp], [t0].[Surname], [t0].[TenantId], [t0].[UserName], CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [UpdatedDailyTasks] AS [u]
        WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([u].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([t].[Id] = [u].[DailyTaskId])) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
FROM (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Comment], [d].[DeadLine], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[EntryDate], [d].[Name], [d].[TaskStatus]
    FROM [DailyTasks] AS [d]
    WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
    ORDER BY [d].[Name]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY

        SELECT 1
        FROM [UpdatedDailyTasks] AS [u]
        WHERE (((@__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([u].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([t].[Id] = [u].[DailyTaskId])) AND ([u].[DailyTaskId] = [t].[Id])) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
FROM (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Comment], [d].[DeadLine], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[EntryDate], [d].[Name], [d].[TaskStatus]
    FROM [DailyTasks] AS [d]
    WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
    ORDER BY [d].[Name]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[AuthenticationSource], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[DeleterUserId], [a].[DeletionTime], [a].[EmailAddress], [a].[EmailConfirmationCode], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsEmailConfirmed], [a].[IsLockoutEnabled], [a].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[Password], [a].[PasswordResetCode], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[Surname], [a].[TenantId], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [AbpUsers] AS [a]
    WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ((@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_3))
) AS [t0] ON [t].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Name]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[TaskStatus], [t].[Comment], [t].[DeadLine], [t].[EntryDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AccessFailedCount], [t0].[AuthenticationSource], [t0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[DeleterUserId], [t0].[DeletionTime], [t0].[EmailAddress], [t0].[EmailConfirmationCode], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsEmailConfirmed], [t0].[IsLockoutEnabled], [t0].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [t0].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [t0].[LastModificationTime], [t0].[LastModifierUserId], [t0].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [t0].[Name], [t0].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [t0].[NormalizedUserName], [t0].[Password], [t0].[PasswordResetCode], [t0].[PhoneNumber], [t0].[SecurityStamp], [t0].[Surname], [t0].[TenantId], [t0].[UserName], CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [UpdatedDailyTasks] AS [u]
        WHERE (((@__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([u].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([t].[Id] = [u].[DailyTaskId])) AND ([u].[DailyTaskId] = [t].[Id])) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
FROM (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Comment], [d].[DeadLine], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[EntryDate], [d].[Name], [d].[TaskStatus]
    FROM [DailyTasks] AS [d]
    WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
    ORDER BY [d].[Name]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY

) AS [t0] ON [t].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Name]

DECLARE @inserted1 TABLE ([Id] int, [_Position] [int]);
MERGE [UpdatedDailyTasks] USING (
VALUES (@p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, @p24, 0),
(@p25, @p26, @p27, @p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, @p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, 1),
(@p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, @p40, @p41, @p42, @p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, 2)) AS i ([CreationTime], [CreatorUserId], [DailyTaskId], [DeleterUserId], [DeletionTime], [IsDeleted], [LastModificationTime], [LastModifierUserId], [MediaFileName], [Note], [OriginalMediaFileName], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([CreationTime], [CreatorUserId], [DailyTaskId], [DeleterUserId], [DeletionTime], [IsDeleted], [LastModificationTime], [LastModifierUserId], [MediaFileName], [Note], [OriginalMediaFileName])
VALUES (i.[CreationTime], i.[CreatorUserId], i.[DailyTaskId], i.[DeleterUserId], i.[DeletionTime], i.[IsDeleted], i.[LastModificationTime], i.[LastModifierUserId], i.[MediaFileName], i.[Note], i.[OriginalMediaFileName])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted1;

SELECT [i].[Id] FROM @inserted1 i
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[TaskStatus], [t].[Comment], [t].[DeadLine], [t].[EntryDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AccessFailedCount], [t0].[AuthenticationSource], [t0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[DeleterUserId], [t0].[DeletionTime], [t0].[EmailAddress], [t0].[EmailConfirmationCode], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsEmailConfirmed], [t0].[IsLockoutEnabled], [t0].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [t0].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [t0].[LastModificationTime], [t0].[LastModifierUserId], [t0].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [t0].[Name], [t0].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [t0].[NormalizedUserName], [t0].[Password], [t0].[PasswordResetCode], [t0].[PhoneNumber], [t0].[SecurityStamp], [t0].[Surname], [t0].[TenantId], [t0].[UserName], CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [UpdatedDailyTasks] AS [u]
        WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([u].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([t].[Id] = [u].[DailyTaskId])) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
FROM (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Comment], [d].[DeadLine], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[EntryDate], [d].[Name], [d].[TaskStatus]
    FROM [DailyTasks] AS [d]
    WHERE (((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([d].[EmployeeId] = @__AbpSession_UserId_0)
    ORDER BY [d].[Name]
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[TaskStatus], [t].[Comment], [t].[DeadLine], [t].[EntryDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AccessFailedCount], [t0].[AuthenticationSource], [t0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[DeleterUserId], [t0].[DeletionTime], [t0].[EmailAddress], [t0].[EmailConfirmationCode], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsEmailConfirmed], [t0].[IsLockoutEnabled], [t0].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [t0].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [t0].[LastModificationTime], [t0].[LastModifierUserId], [t0].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [t0].[Name], [t0].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [t0].[NormalizedUserName], [t0].[Password], [t0].[PasswordResetCode], [t0].[PhoneNumber], [t0].[SecurityStamp], [t0].[Surname], [t0].[TenantId], [t0].[UserName], CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [UpdatedDailyTasks] AS [u]
        WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([u].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([t].[Id] = [u].[DailyTaskId])) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END
FROM (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[Comment], [d].[DeadLine], [d].[EmployeeId], [d].[EntryDate], [d].[Name], [d].[TaskStatus]
    FROM [DailyTasks] AS [d]
    WHERE (((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([d].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ([d].[EmployeeId] = @__AbpSession_UserId_0)
    ORDER BY [d].[Name]
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[AuthenticationSource], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[DeleterUserId], [a].[DeletionTime], [a].[EmailAddress], [a].[EmailConfirmationCode], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsEmailConfirmed], [a].[IsLockoutEnabled], [a].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[Password], [a].[PasswordResetCode], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[Surname], [a].[TenantId], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [AbpUsers] AS [a]
    WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ((@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_3))
) AS [t0] ON [t].[EmployeeId] = [t0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Name]
